        "content": "Bell had just turned the key in her lock, her hand trembling slightly as the tumblers clicked. The sound of your footsteps descending the stairs had felt like a countdown, each one pulling at something in her chest. She'd pressed her back against the door, eyes squeezed shut, trying to memorize the warmth of your embrace, the way your voice had sounded when you said those three words—*I love you*—like they were the easiest thing in the world to say.\n\nHer phone buzzes in her pocket, the vibration startling against her hip. She fumbles for it, nearly dropping it in her haste, and when she sees your name on the screen, a breathless, disbelieving laugh escapes her.\n\n\"You—\" She starts, but her voice cracks. She clears her throat, turning away from her door and sliding down to sit on the hallway floor, her back against the wall, legs stretched out in front of her. \"You absolute *dork*.\"\n\nBut she's smiling. God, she's smiling so hard her cheeks hurt, and she can't stop it even if she wanted to.\n\n\"Clingy? Me?\" She scoffs into the phone, though the sound is watery, thick with emotion she's trying desperately to mask with her usual bravado. \"I was just being polite, making sure you didn't trip down the stairs and break your neck. Can't have my boyfriend dying on day one. Bad look for me.\"\n\nThe word *boyfriend* slips out naturally, and she pauses, her breath catching. She said it. She *said* it. And it doesn't feel wrong. It feels... terrifyingly right.\n\n\"But yeah,\" she continues, her voice dropping to something softer, more intimate, like she's sharing a secret with you across the distance. \"Talk to me. Tell me about... I don't know. What you see. What you're thinking. Just... don't hang up yet, okay?\"\n\nShe pulls her knees up to her chest, wrapping one arm around them while keeping the phone pressed to her ear. The hallway is still cold and clinical, but your voice in her ear makes it bearable.\n\n\"And Sakuta?\" She adds, her voice barely above a whisper. \"I... I love you too. You idiot.\""
